-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2. 지속적 배포, CD</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Continuous Delivery</p>\n<ul>\n<li>패키지화 된 결과물 실행 환경에 수동 반영</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Continuous Deplyment</p>\n<ul>\n<li>자동 배포</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Pipe line</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-카나리-배포와-블루그린-배포\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%B9%B4%EB%82%98%EB%A6%AC-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%EC%99%80-%EB%B8%94%EB%A3%A8%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%B0-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC\" aria-label=\"3 카나리 배포와 블루그린 배포 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>3. 카나리 배포와 블루그린 배포</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>카나리 배포(Canary Deployment)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>새 애플리케이션을 소수에게 배포한 후 안정성이 확보되면 점진적으로 모든 사용자에게 배포</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>블루-그린 배포(Blue-Green Deployment)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>두 개의 환경(Blue: 기존 버전, Green: 새로운 버전)을 동시에 운영하여 새로운 버전이 준비되면 한번에 모든 트래픽을 이동시키는 방식</li>\n<li>rollback 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-DevOps\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-DevOps\" aria-label=\"4 DevOps permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>4. DevOps</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>소프트웨어 개발(Development)과 운영(Operations)을 통합하는 문화 및 방법론</li>\n<li><strong>자동화</strong>, <strong>협업</strong>, 지속적 통합/배포(CI/CD)를 통해 <strong>빠르고 안정적인 소프트웨어 개발 및 운영을 목표</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"5-Container-가상화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-Container-%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"5 Container 가상화 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>5. Container 가상화</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>운영체제(OS) 수준에서 애플리케이션을 격리하고 실행하는 가상화 기술</li>\n<li>하이퍼바이저 기반 VM(Virtual Machine) 보다 <strong>더 가볍고 빠르며, 확장성이 뛰어남</strong></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 Cloud Native Application","date":"January 13, 2025","update":"January 13, 2025","tags":["MSA","Cloud Native Application"],"series":"🍃 Microservice와 Spring Cloud"},"fields":{"slug":"/microservice_post_1/","readingTime":{"minutes":0.84}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"d80064a3-dcd1-5c2d-ae4a-55d766002076","fields":{"slug":"/microservice_post/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 Cloud Native Architecture"}}},{"node":{"id":"c946e328-4776-5cd6-be34-87d833402d2e","fields":{"slug":"/microservice_post_1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 Cloud Native Application"}}},{"node":{"id":"3ba591bd-f884-5266-91d2-12d30e93343a","fields":{"slug":"/microservice_post_2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 12 Factors"}}},{"node":{"id":"4fe26e87-179f-52be-81cd-b428af7f7b6b","fields":{"slug":"/250120_VS/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 Monolithic VS MSA"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/microservice_post/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 Cloud Native Architecture"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/microservice_post_2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍃 12 Factors"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"c946e328-4776-5cd6-be34-87d833402d2e","series":"🍃 Microservice와 Spring Cloud","previousPostId":"d80064a3-dcd1-5c2d-ae4a-55d766002076","nextPostId":"3ba591bd-f884-5266-91d2-12d30e93343a"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}